summary: do you ever fall into a hole. like a hole that is filled with someone. like the next thing you know you're watching these videos...
body: do you ever fall into a hole. like a hole that is filled with someone. like the next thing you know you’re watching these videos and listening to these songs that speak to your soul and you are slowly falling in love. and you’ve spent almost 8 hours looking at this person in interviews and watching him interact with fans and you watch them sing and watch them be an amazing person. and you just. i dont know, fall in love with someone who you will never meet? and it hurts watching and listening to them because you truly have feelings for this person? yeah.
